OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FOne of the world's biggest and most
OL,7,Fanticipated sporting events, the FIFA
OL,8,FWorld Cup, is rapidly approaching.
OL,10,FFrom a new 48-team format to new rules
OL,11,Fand the first-ever halftime show,
OL,12,Fthere is a lot for fans to keep up
OL,13,Fwith ahead of kick-off.
OL,15,FITV News breaks down everything you
OL,16,Fneed to know about the tournament, and
OL,17,Fwhat to expect as football's biggest
OL,18,Fevent heads to the United States,
OL,19,FCanada, and Mexico.
OL,21,FWhen and where is the World Cup?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
