OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780931475
OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThe tournament will run from June 11
OL,7,Fto July 26 and will be played across
OL,8,Fthe US, Canada and Mexico.
OL,10,FA total of 104 games will be played at
OL,11,F11 sites in US, three in Mexico and
OL,12,Ftwo in Canada.
OL,14,FIn keeping with tradition, all three
OL,15,Fhost nations automatically qualified
OL,16,Ffor the tournament.
OL,18,FWhere and when will the final take
OL,19,Fplace - and who is favourite to win?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
