OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780931475
OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThe final will take place at the New
OL,7,FYork New Jersey (MetLife) Stadium,
OL,8,Fwhich has a capacity of 82,500 people.
OL,10,FIt is also home to the American
OL,11,Ffootball teams, the New York Giants
OL,12,Fand the New York Jets.
OL,14,FAccording to the bookies, the six
OL,15,Flikeliest teams to lift the World Cup
OL,16,Ftrophy are Spain, France, England,
OL,17,FBrazil, Argentina, and Portugal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
