OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FHowever, a German economist who has
OL,7,Fpredicted the World Cup winners
OL,8,Fcorrectly since 2014 has pegged The
OL,9,FNetherlands to win.
OL,11,FJoachim Klement, who uses a complex
OL,12,Fforecast model to make his
OL,13,Fpredictions, also said England are due
OL,14,Fto make it to the semi-finals, with
OL,15,FPortugal poised to knock them out,
OL,16,Faccording to the BBC.
OL,18,FWhen and where are England and
OL,19,FScotland playing?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
