OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FEngland, whose training camp is in
OL,7,FKansas City, will play all three of
OL,8,Ftheir group games in the United States.
OL,10,FScotland, whose training camp is in
OL,11,FCharlotte, North Carolina, will also
OL,12,Fplay all their group games in the US.
OL,14,FWill pubs in the UK be open late for
OL,15,Fthe games?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
