OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FPubs in England and Wales are allowed
OL,7,Fto stay open until 1am for England or
OL,8,FScotland matches in the knockout
OL,9,Fstages that kick off between 5pm and
OL,10,F9pm, and until 2am for kick-offs
OL,11,Fbetween 9pm and 10pm.
OL,13,FThis decision came after the
OL,14,Fgovernment launched a public
OL,15,Fconsultation on extending pub
OL,16,Flicensing hours, especially for the
OL,17,Ftournament.
OL,19,FHow will the group stages work?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
