OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThis is the first World Cup tournament
OL,7,Fthat will feature 48 teams as opposed
OL,8,Fto the usual 32.
OL,10,FThis means the format will also look
OL,11,Fdifferent: There will be 12 groups of
OL,12,Ffour, with the top two teams ` plus
OL,13,Fthe eight best third-place teams `
OL,14,Fmoving on to create a Round of 32.
OL,16,FFrom the Round of 32 onwards, the
OL,17,Ftournament follows the classic
OL,18,Fknockout system: Round of 32, Round of
OL,19,F16, quarter-finals, semi-finals and
OL,20,Fthe final.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
