PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780931475
OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThis means the eventual champions will
OL,7,Fplay seven matches in total ` three in
OL,8,Fthe group stage and four in the
OL,9,Fknockout rounds.
OL,11,FHow do third-place teams qualify for
OL,12,Fthe round of 32?
OL,14,FThe eight best third-place teams in
OL,15,Fthe group stages will advance into the
OL,16,Fknock-out stages.
OL,18,FThis is calculated based on who has
OL,19,Fthe greatest number of points obtained
OL,20,Fin the group matches after the top two
OL,21,Fteams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
