OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FIf teams are tied, officials will look
OL,7,Fat superior goal difference.
OL,9,FWho will perform at the half-time show?
OL,11,FAnother first for this year's
OL,12,Ftournament is that, similar to the the
OL,13,FNFL Superbowl, there will be a
OL,14,Fhalftime show during the World Cup
OL,15,Ffinal.
OL,17,FMadonna, Shakira, and K-pop boyband
OL,18,FBTS are all set to perform on July 19,
OL,19,Fwith cameos by characters from Sesame
OL,20,FStreet and The Muppets, according to
OL,21,FFIFA.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
