OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FOther characters likely to make an
OL,7,Fappearance are the mascots of the
OL,8,Fthree host nations: Maple the moose,
OL,9,FZayu the jaguar and Clutch the bald
OL,10,Feagle will represent host countries
OL,11,FCanada, Mexico and America
OL,12,Frespectively.
OL,14,FAre there any new rules?
OL,16,FThe tournament will also see a few new
OL,17,Frules, including new countdowns on
OL,18,Fgoal kicks, throw-ins and
OL,19,Fsubstitutions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
