OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThese changes are being introduced to
OL,7,Faddress loss of tempo in matches and
OL,8,Fto cut down on time-wasting. They are
OL,9,Fas follows:
OL,11,FAt the end of April, the International
OL,12,FFootball Association Board (IFAB) also
OL,13,Fannounced new rules around players who
OL,14,Fcover their mouths while confronting
OL,15,Fopposition players.
OL,17,FThe rules, which it said would also be
OL,18,Fadopted for the World Cup, mean that
OL,19,Fanyone caught doing so may be issued a
OL,20,Fred card.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
