OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThe move comes after Madrid player
OL,7,FVinicius Jr faced unpunished abuse
OL,8,Fduring a Champions League fixture
OL,9,Fagainst Benfica in February.
OL,11,FWhile this isn't a rule, FIFA has
OL,12,Fannounced that it would also include
OL,13,Fthree-minute hydration breaks 22
OL,14,Fminutes into each half of every game
OL,15,Fto help players with hazardous heat
OL,16,Fconditions.
OL,18,FWhat about Iran?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
