OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThe war in the Middle East, which
OL,7,Fbegan in February after a joint US-
OL,8,FIsraeli attack on Iran, has led to
OL,9,Funcertainty around Iran's
OL,10,Fparticipation.
OL,12,FThe US government has said the
OL,13,Fcountry's players will be welcome at
OL,14,Fthe tournament but that players,
OL,15,Fcoaches and officials who have
OL,16,Fcompleted military service with the
OL,17,FIslamic Revolutionary Guard Corps
OL,18,F(IRGC) may face entry restrictions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
