OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FIran's sports minister Ahmad Donyamali
OL,7,Fsaid earlier this month that the
OL,8,Fentire Iran squad will be given visas,
OL,9,Fsaying: "The FIFA president promised
OL,10,Fus that all our players would receive
OL,11,Fvisas."
OL,13,F"There is no reason why our players
OL,14,Fshould not receive visas," he added.
OL,16,FThe team has been training in Turkey
OL,17,Fand is set to play its first game
OL,18,Fagainst New Zealand in Los Angeles on
OL,19,FJune 15.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
