PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780931475
OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Everything you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FHowever, the team is relocating its
OL,7,Ftraining base from Tucson, Arizona, to
OL,8,FTijuana, Mexico, to which Mexico's
OL,9,FPresident, Claudia Sheinbaum, said:
OL,10,F"We have no problem."
OL,12,F"The United States does not want the
OL,13,FIranian team to stay overnight, but
OL,14,Fthey are going to play three matches
OL,15,Fthere," she said.
OL,17,F"So they asked us: 'Can they stay
OL,18,Fovernight in Mexico?' And we said:
OL,19,F'Yes, no problem.'"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
